These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, american, pakistani, british, australian, japanese, colombian
1. the american is in the middle##1
2. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the australian is on the right of the british##1
4. the canadian is on the right of the pakistani##1
5. the colombian is on the far left##1
6. the japanese is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | colombian | british | australian | american | pakistani | canadian | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, photographer, firefighter, chef, bartender, dancer, coach
1. the coach is on the far right##1
2. the architect is on the far left##1
3. the architect is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the bartender is on the left of the firefighter##1
5. the chef is on the right of the dancer##1
6. the coach is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | architect | bartender | firefighter | dancer | chef | photographer | coach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, baking, video-games, collecting, camping, skydiving, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | camping | writing | skydiving | video-games | traveling | baking | collecting |

 #################################

 
