4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | goat | pony | rat | horse | hamster | fish | cat |

