1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts | mystery | epic | spy | scientific | time-travel |

